<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>美股收盘日报｜{{ data.date }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-page: rgb(223, 239, 224);
            --bg-card: rgba(223, 239, 224, 0.92);
            --border-card: rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.18);
            --shadow-card: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --text-main: #1a1a1a;
            --text-muted: #5c5c5c;
            --accent: #2d6a4f;
            --accent-2: #3a7d5e;
            --danger: #c0392b;
            --warn: #b8860b;
            --info: #2471a3;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgb(223, 239, 224) 0%, rgb(210, 232, 215) 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 980px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f, #3a7d5e);
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 28px 32px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: .92;
            color: #f3f9f6;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 28px 0 16px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin: 18px 0 12px;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        h4 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin: 12px 0 10px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .section {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
            padding: 22px 24px;
            margin: 18px 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px 18px;
        }

        .timeline .card {
            background: rgb(223, 239, 224);
            border: 1px solid rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.18);
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .timeline h5 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .timeline p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #2f2f2f;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 14px 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        th {
            background: rgba(223, 239, 224, 0.95);
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(odd) {
            background: transparent;
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.035);
        }

        tbody tr:hover {
            background: rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.08);
        }

        .positive {
            color: var(--accent-2);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .negative {
            color: var(--danger);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .neutral {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .green {
            color: var(--accent-2);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .red {
            color: var(--danger);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .summary-box {
            background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.25);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 18px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.25);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 14px 0;
        }

        .warning {
            background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.25);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 14px 0;
        }

        .success {
            background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.25);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 14px 0;
        }

        .source {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding: 18px 0 6px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>📈 美股收盘日报｜{{ data.date }}</h1>
            <p>专业、简洁、高信息密度 · 每日10分钟掌握美股核心动态</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 0. 今日一句话总结 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🎯 今日一句话总结</h2>
            <div class="summary-box">
                <p><strong>今日市场状态：</strong>{{ market_summary }}</p>
                <p><strong>核心驱动因素：</strong>{{ market_driver }}</p>
                <p><strong>资金情绪：</strong>{{ market_sentiment }}</p>
                <p><strong>最值得关注主线：</strong>{{ main_focus }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 1. 大盘表现总览 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>📊 1.大盘表现总览</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>指数</th>
                        <th>收盘点位</th>
                        <th>涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>日内高低点</th>
                        <th>成交量变化</th>
                        <th>技术状态</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for name, index in data.indices.items() %}
                    {% if name != "VIX" %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ index.price|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if index.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif index.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if index.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ index.change_pct|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ index.low|round(2) }} - {{ index.high|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ index.volume|number_format }}</td>
                        <td>{{ technical_status(name, index) }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 2. 盘中走势复盘 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>⏰ 2.盘中走势复盘</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
                <h4>📈 时间线复盘：</h4>
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>🌅 盘前</h5>
                    <p>{{ pre_market }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>🏁 开盘</h5>
                    <p>{{ opening }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>🕐 午盘</h5>
                    <p>{{ midday }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h5>🌅 尾盘</h5>
                    <p>{{ closing }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>🎯 核心原因分析：</h4>
                <p>{{ core_reason }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 3. 宏观环境 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🌍 3.宏观环境</h2>
            
            <!-- 3.1 美债收益率 -->
            <h3>3.1 美债收益率</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>项目</th>
                        <th>最新水平</th>
                        <th>日变化</th>
                        <th>市场含义</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for name, bond in data.macro.items() %}
                    {% if name in ["10Y收益率", "30Y收益率", "13T国债", "5Y Treasury"] %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ bond.price|round(3) }}%</td>
                        <td class="{% if bond.change_pct != '暂无' and bond.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif bond.change_pct != '暂无' and bond.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if bond.change_pct != '暂无' %}{% if bond.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ bond.change_pct|round(2) }}%{% else %}暂无{% endif %}
                        </td>
                        <td>自动分析暂缺</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>📊 债市分析：</h4>
                <p>{{ bond_analysis_summary }}</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 3.2 Fed 降息预期 -->
            <h3>3.2 Fed 降息预期</h3>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>🔍 CME FedWatch 数据：</h4>
                <p><strong>下次FOMC降息概率：</strong>{{ fed_rate_cut_probability }}%</p>
                <p><strong>年内预期降息次数：</strong>{{ expected_rate_cuts }}次</p>
                <p><strong>较前一日变化：</strong>{{ fed_change }}</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 3.3 美元、黄金、原油、比特币 -->
            <h3>3.3 美元、黄金、原油、加密货币</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>资产</th>
                        <th>最新价格</th>
                        <th>涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>含义</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for name, asset in data.macro.items() %}
                    {% if name in ["美元指数DXY", "黄金", "WTI原油", "比特币", "以太坊"] %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ asset.price }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if asset.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif asset.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if asset.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ asset.change_pct|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>自动分析暂缺</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 4. 板块表现 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🏢 4.板块表现</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>排名</th>
                        <th>板块</th>
                        <th>ETF</th>
                        <th>当日涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>近5日</th>
                        <th>近1月</th>
                        <th>跑赢/跑输标普</th>
                        <th>主要驱动</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for sector in sectors_performance %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ loop.index }}</td>
                        <td>{{ sector.name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ sector.etf }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if sector.change > 0 %}positive{% elif sector.change < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if sector.change > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ sector.change|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ sector.change_5d|round(2) }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ sector.change_1m|round(2) }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ sector.vs_sp500 }}</td>
                        <td>{{ sector.driver }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>🎯 板块分析：</h4>
                <p>{{ sector_analysis }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 5. 主题与风格表现 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🎯 5.主题与风格表现</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>主题/风格</th>
                        <th>代表ETF</th>
                        <th>当日涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>近5日</th>
                        <th>近1月</th>
                        <th>解读</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for theme in themes_performance %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ theme.name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ theme.etf }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if theme.change > 0 %}positive{% elif theme.change < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if theme.change > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ theme.change|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ theme.change_5d|round(2) }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ theme.change_1m|round(2) }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ theme.analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>🔍 主题分析：</h4>
                <p>{{ theme_analysis }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 6. 市场宽度与参与度 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>📊 市场宽度与参与度</h2>
            
            <!-- 6.1 均线参与度 -->
            <h3>6.1 均线参与度</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>指数/市场</th>
                        <th>高于20日均线比例</th>
                        <th>高于50日均线比例</th>
                        <th>高于100日均线比例</th>
                        <th>高于200日均线比例</th>
                        <th>解读</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>S&P 500</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_20_sp500 }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_50_sp500 }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_100_sp500 }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_200_sp500 }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_20_sp500_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Nasdaq 100</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_20_qqq }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_50_qqq }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_100_qqq }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_200_qqq }}%</td>
                        <td>{{ ma_20_qqq_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- 6.2 涨跌家数、新高新低 -->
            <h3>6.2 涨跌家数、新高新低</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>指标</th>
                        <th>NYSE</th>
                        <th>Nasdaq</th>
                        <th>解读</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>上涨家数</td>
                        <td>{{ nyse_advance }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_advance }}</td>
                        <td>{{ breadth_advance_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>下跌家数</td>
                        <td>{{ nyse_decline }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_decline }}</td>
                        <td>{{ breadth_decline_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>涨跌比</td>
                        <td>{{ nyse_ratio }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_ratio }}</td>
                        <td>{{ breadth_ratio_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>创52周新高数量</td>
                        <td>{{ nyda_new_highs }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_new_highs }}</td>
                        <td>{{ new_highs_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>创52周新低数量</td>
                        <td>{{ nyda_new_lows }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_new_lows }}</td>
                        <td>{{ new_lows_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 7. 技术面分析 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>📈 7.技术面分析</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>标的</th>
                        <th>当前价格</th>
                        <th>20日线</th>
                        <th>50日线</th>
                        <th>100日线</th>
                        <th>200日线</th>
                        <th>RSI</th>
                        <th>MACD</th>
                        <th>关键支撑</th>
                        <th>关键压力</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for tech in technical_analysis %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ tech.symbol }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.price|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.ma20|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.ma50|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.ma100|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.ma200|round(2) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.rsi }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.macd }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.support }}</td>
                        <td>{{ tech.resistance }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>🎯 技术要点：</h4>
                <p>{{ technical_key_points }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 8. 重点个股新闻与异动 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🔥 8.重点个股新闻与异动</h2>
            
            <!-- 8.1 大型科技七巨头 -->
            <h3>8.1 大型科技七巨头</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>股票</th>
                        <th>涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>原因</th>
                        <th>技术位置</th>
                        <th>后续关注</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for stock in magnificent_7 %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ stock.symbol }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if stock.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif stock.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if stock.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ stock.change_pct|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ stock.reason }}</td>
                        <td>{{ stock.technical }}</td>
                        <td>{{ stock.watch }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- 8.2 AI硬件/半导体 -->
            <h3>8.2 AI硬件/半导体</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>股票</th>
                        <th>涨跌幅</th>
                        <th>原因</th>
                        <th>技术位置</th>
                        <th>后续关注</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for stock in ai_hardware %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ stock.symbol }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if stock.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif stock.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if stock.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ stock.change_pct|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ stock.reason }}</td>
                        <td>{{ stock.technical }}</td>
                        <td>{{ stock.watch }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 9. 财报日历与财报解读 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>📊 9.财报日历与财报解读</h2>
            
            <!-- 9.1 昨夜已公布财报的重点公司 -->
            <h3>9.1 昨夜已公布财报的重点公司</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>公司</th>
                        <th>收入</th>
                        <th>EPS</th>
                        <th>是否beat指引</th>
                        <th>盘后反应</th>
                        <th>核心解读</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for earnings in recent_earnings %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ earnings.company }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.revenue }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.eps }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.beat_guidance }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if earnings.after_hours > 0 %}positive{% elif earnings.after_hours < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if earnings.after_hours > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ earnings.after_hours|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <!-- 9.2 接下来1-3个交易日重要财报 -->
            <h3>9.2 接下来1-3个交易日重要财报</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>日期</th>
                        <th>公司</th>
                        <th>市场关注点</th>
                        <th>可能影响板块</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for earnings in upcoming_earnings %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ earnings.date }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.company }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.focus }}</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings.impact }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 10. 机构观点与资金流 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>💼 10.机构观点与资金流</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>机构/来源</th>
                        <th>观点</th>
                        <th>涉及资产</th>
                        <th>市场影响</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for view in institutional_views %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ view.institution }}</td>
                        <td>{{ view.viewpoint }}</td>
                        <td>{{ view.assets }}</td>
                        <td>{{ view.impact }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 11. 板块轮动判断 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🎯 11.板块轮动判断</h2>
            <div class="highlight">
                <h4>当前市场状态：</h4>
                <p>{{ market_state }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>📊 资金流向：</h4>
                <p><strong>主要流入：</strong>{{ money_flow_in }}</p>
                <p><strong>主要流出：</strong>{{ money_flow_out }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>🔍 主线判断：</h4>
                <p>{{ main_line_analysis }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 12. 我的重点关注股观察 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🔍 12.我的重点关注股观察</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>股票</th>
                        <th>当日涨跌</th>
                        <th>当前趋势</th>
                        <th>关键新闻</th>
                        <th>支撑位</th>
                        <th>压力位</th>
                        <th>我的判断</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for focus in focus_stocks %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ focus.symbol }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if focus.change_pct > 0 %}positive{% elif focus.change_pct < 0 %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {% if focus.change_pct > 0 %}+{% endif %}{{ focus.change_pct|round(2) }}%
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ focus.trend }}</td>
                        <td>{{ focus.news }}</td>
                        <td>{{ focus.support }}</td>
                        <td>{{ focus.resistance }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if focus.judgment == '继续强势' %}positive{% elif focus.judgment == '破位风险' %}negative{% else %}neutral{% endif %}">
                            {{ focus.judgment }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 13. 明日交易计划/观察清单 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>📅 13.明日交易计划/观察清单</h2>
            
            <!-- 13.1 宏观观察 -->
            <h3>13.1 宏观观察</h3>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>🔍 关键观察点：</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>10Y美债收益率：</strong>{{ ten_yield_observation }}</li>
                    <li><strong>美元指数方向：</strong>{{ dollar_observation }}</li>
                    <li><strong>油价/黄金/VIX：</strong>{{ commodity_observation }}</li>
                    <li><strong>Fed官员讲话：</strong>{{ fed_speech_observation }}</li>
                    <tr>
                        <td>创52周新高数量</td>
                        <td>{{ nyda_new_highs }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_new_highs }}</td>
                        <td>{{ new_highs_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>创52周新低数量</td>
                        <td>{{ nyda_new_lows }}</td>
                        <td>{{ nasdaq_new_lows }}</td>
                        <td>{{ new_lows_analysis }}</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
		
        <!-- 14. 风险提示 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>⚠️14.风险提示</h2>
            <div class="warning">
                <h4>当前市场最大风险：</h4>
                <p>{{ main_risk }}</p>
            </div>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>风险维度</th>
                        <th>当前状态</th>
                        <th>风险等级</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>宏观利率</td>
                        <td>{{ macro_rate_status }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if macro_risk_level == '高' %}negative{% elif macro_risk_level == '中高' %}neutral{% else %}positive{% endif %}">
                            {{ macro_risk_level }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>市场宽度</td>
                        <td>{{ breadth_status }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if breadth_risk_level == '高' %}negative{% elif breadth_risk_level == '中高' %}neutral{% else %}positive{% endif %}">
                            {{ breadth_risk_level }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>AI拥挤度</td>
                        <td>{{ ai_crowding_status }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if ai_crowding_risk_level == '高' %}negative{% elif ai_crowding_risk_level == '中高' %}neutral{% else %}positive{% endif %}">
                            {{ ai_crowding_risk_level }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>财报风险</td>
                        <td>{{ earnings_risk_status }}</td>
                        <td class="{% if earnings_risk_level == '高' %}negative{% elif earnings_risk_level == '中高' %}neutral{% else %}positive{% endif %}">
                            {{ earnings_risk_level }}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <br><hr>

        <!-- 15. 最终结论 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>🎯 15.最终结论</h2>
            <div class="summary-box">
                <h4>📈 今日市场结论</h4>
                <p>{{ market_conclusion }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>🔍 当前市场阶段</h4>
                <p>{{ market_phase }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h4>💼 我的操作倾向</h4>
                <p>{{ trading_bias }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="success">
                <h4>🎯 最值得关注的5个信号</h4>
                <ul>
                    {% for signal in key_signals %}
                    <li>{{ signal }}</li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>📊 Data Source：Yahoo Finance | 📧 Created by：Nekomini Bot | 📅 {{ generated_at }}（北京时间UTC+8）</p>
            <p>power by Nekomini</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>